torchy blane in panama is a 1938 american mystery film directed by william clemens . it stars lola lane , paul kelly , and tom kennedy . it was released on may 7 , 1938 . this is the fifth film in a series of " torchy blane " movies by warner bros. and is followed by torchy gets her man . torchy , steve , and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; are on the trail of a bank robber aboard an ocean liner traveling from new york to los angeles via the panama canal .